## [1.1] - 2016-02-23
- Always install headers of third-party packages into a subdirectory of
  includedir.
- Fixed SUN stlport build issue where "-library=stlport4" was misinterpreted as
  a library name.

## [1.0] - 2016-02-19
- Added versioning support -- wscript in project repos now can specify
  `min_bde_tools_version` and `max_bde_tools_version`
